#### 2. 优化工具查找性能

**位置**: `internal/permission/policy.go:188-195`

**建议**:
```go
var knownToolsMap map[string]bool

func init() {
    knownToolsMap = make(map[string]bool, len(knownTools))
    for _, tool := range knownTools {
        knownToolsMap[tool] = true
    }
}

func isKnownTool(tool string) bool {
    return knownToolsMap[tool]
}
```

**原因**: 将线性查找 O(n) 优化为常数查找 O(1)，对频繁调用场景有性能提升

